race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: JET BOOTS TOMMY (8) is a promising dog in the frame at 12 of 30 starts including eight wins and was in the minors again latest (22.57) over 400m at Maitland. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. STOLE MY BONE (1) was a Grade 5 winner two back at Muswellbrook then although missed the placings finished on the winners' heels when fourth (19.42) at Muswellbrook. Expecting significant improvement this line-up. RETURN AN EARN (2) had the drop on the lead from the squeeze box before taking over turning, drawing clear to score (17.69) at this track in a Grade 5 over 300m. One of the prime contenders. PARK KEY PAW (3) has claims fresh from a recent placing.
